"``p2`` 和 ``p3``："

#: ../../docs/tutorials/math/beziers_and_curves.rst:68
msgid ""
"We apply a linear interpolation to each couple of points to reduce them to "
"three:"
msgstr "我们对每两个点进行线性插值，将它们减少到三个："

